trans-unit.source: Indicates how an assembly should be produced.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvordan en samling skal produseres.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibConverter.ConvertTypeLibToAssembly%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
Imports a type library for any platform.
trans-unit.target: Importerer et typebibliotek for alle plattformer.

trans-unit.source: Imports a library for the ARM platform.
Imports a type library for the Itanium platform.
Imports a type library for the x86 64-bit platform.
trans-unit.target: Importerer et typebibliotek for x86 64-biters plattform.

trans-unit.source: Imports a type library for the x86 platform.
trans-unit.target: Importerer et typebibliotek for x86 plattformen.

trans-unit.source: Prevents inclusion of a version resource in the interop assembly.
trans-unit.target: Hindrer inkludering av en versjonsressurs i assembly-fil.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder.DefineVersionInfoResource%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder.DefineVersionInfoResource%2A?displayProperty=fullName> metoden.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.PrimaryInteropAssemblyAttribute"></xref> attribute.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.PrimaryInteropAssemblyAttribute"> </xref> attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Imports all <xref uid="langword_csharp_SAFEARRAY" name="SAFEARRAY" href=""></xref> instances as <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> instead of typed, single-dimensional, zero-based managed arrays.
trans-unit.target: Importerer alle <xref uid="langword_csharp_SAFEARRAY" name="SAFEARRAY" href=""> </xref> forekomster som <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> i stedet for typeangitt, én filterkontekstens, nullbasert administrerte matriser.

trans-unit.source: This option is useful when dealing with multi-dimensional, non-zero-based <xref uid="langword_csharp_SAFEARRAY" name="SAFEARRAY" href=""></xref> instances, which otherwise cannot be accessed unless you edit the resulting assembly by using the MSIL Disassembler (Ildasm.exe) and MSIL Assembler (Ilasm.exe) tools.
trans-unit.target: Dette alternativet er nyttig når håndtering av flerdimensjonale, ikke-null-baserte <xref uid="langword_csharp_SAFEARRAY" name="SAFEARRAY" href=""> </xref> forekomster som ellers er ikke tilgjengelig med mindre du redigerer resulterende samlingen ved hjelp av MSIL Disassembler (Ildasm.exe) og verktøy for MSIL Assembler (Ilasm.exe).

trans-unit.source: Transforms <xref uid="langword_csharp_[out, retval]" name="[out, retval]" href=""></xref> parameters of methods on dispatch-only interfaces ([dispinterface](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e8c18ae5-3d9e-4dff-aa20-b5acc723eacf)) into return values.
trans-unit.target: Overfører <xref uid="langword_csharp_[out, retval]" name="[out, retval]" href=""> </xref> parameterne for metoder på bare angitte grensesnitt ([visningsgrensesnitt](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e8c18ae5-3d9e-4dff-aa20-b5acc723eacf)) til å returnere verdier.

trans-unit.source: Imports all interfaces as interfaces that suppress the common language runtime's stack crawl for <xref:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode?displayProperty=fullName> permission.
trans-unit.target: Importerer alle grensesnitt som grensesnitt som undertrykke common language runtime's stakk kravlesøk <xref:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode?displayProperty=fullName> tillatelse.

trans-unit.source: Be sure you understand the responsibilities associated with suppressing this security check.
trans-unit.target: Pass på at du forstår ansvaret som er knyttet til undertrykking sikkerhetskontrollen.
